{
  "stem": "10644.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, horse has been for us a delicacy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in this was the only-- only protein what we could get.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It has a little taste.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We know, because it could have so-called hippuric acid, it just-- acidity of this hippuric acid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise, it is-- it was perfect food what our body needed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I recall that I took the pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the fire, you know, fire for me and for my friend, Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Kronsohn, we both have typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He has complication with the heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I start to feel pains in my legs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Next day, we-- somebody gets out and say there is a Russian officer outside-- a Russian soldier-- true-- a Russian soldier.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I hear tremendous amount of [NON-ENGLISH] Russian soldiers-- Russian army passing by, around 300 yards from us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see a road.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They paved the road.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they are passing, you know, one division-- a tremendous amount.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was-- was thinking for that-- oh, they are coming to liberate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was not the easier intentions even at interested in us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were near-- they were going towards Laumberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Two, three miles from Laumberg was a-- a island, Peenemunde, where all the missiles there, German missiles, V1 and V2.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, at the-- end of the war, they had missiles shooting into-- into London-- were-- were built.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was a-- a race between the Russians and the English, English gun coming from-- from the north, Russians coming from the-- from the east.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everybody wanted, you know, to grab this installations-- installations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Russians grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the scientists were already in the hands of the Americans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With another friend, with my friend we moved, you know, we went to-- we went to Laumberg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found an apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans fled-- fled-- but we found their bread or something else to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- was, for us, the main problem-- food, food, food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had enough food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I go to Laumberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spend a few days there with another friend, Paul [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was veterinarian doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we headed-- with-- went to a foot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was much in a better condition than I am.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's a veterinarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He went, you know, to-- to the-- he supplied right away with meat-- meat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then Russians send epidemiological hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A hospital, a administration-- doctors-- doctors and administration to treat people with infectious conditions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're among-- in this-- in this the doctor of the-- this, the doctor, the chief doctor of this unit was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The men who supplied us with all the food was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was also a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Russian Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there are other-- other doctors, not many-- four or five in this whole hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all Russians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I decided-- I-- they-- they brought me without my wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My wife left-- left in-- in-- in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now my-- my-- I got-- I was decided I stay here until I have information about my family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot go to Bialystok, because the Poles take out Jews out of the-- of the trains, and they killed them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Safer here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm-- have Russians here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Poles came, but the Russians-- I'm with-- with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know, [NON-ENGLISH], I have friends-- friends are Russians officers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I treated them for gonorrhea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got sulfa drugs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, from the-- from the hospital-- from the hospital and from the-- from the doctor's office-- office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ending?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ending.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is, how to say, the story-- not the final story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is, you know, right, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I-- I found my wife dead in Eckernforde.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is a city, a port, in Western Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
